TO RUN 'RUN'; FIRST TYPE 'GR' ANDSET THE LO-RES PLOTTING COLOR TOWHATEVER YOU'D LIKE THE SCREENBOUNDARY TO BE. THEN SET X AND Y TOVALID SCREEN COORDINATES. (A GOODSTARTING LOCATION IS X=2 AND Y=37.)THEN TYPE 'GOTO 1' TO START THEGAME.ALTERNATELY; ADD THESE COMMANDS TO ANEWLINE 0 AND RUN IT. AN EXAMPLESTARTING CONFIGURATION IS STORED ONTHIS DISK.USE THE I-J-K-M KEYS TO MOVE. TRY TOESCAPE THE CAGE WITHOUT RUNNING INTOANYTHING.